I was told that I cannot join more then one house, so I want to wait until I decide what house I really want to be a part of.<br>
<br>
What houses have you guys chosen, and on what grounds?<br>
<br>
From what I understand, if you only work on one kind of skills, then you only have a fair chance to advance in one house: Hlaalu if you are a thief, Redoran if you are a fighter, and Telvanni if you are a mage. However, if you use all kinds of skills, then you can just pick any house.<br>
<br>
I don't know what &quot;phat lewts&quot; their different quests givs, if any. But that's a minor concern. I want to go with the coolest house.<br>
<br>
